(8162, 'Miflonide 400mcg 60 inhalation capsule +inhaler', 'ميفلونيد 400مكجم 60 كبسولة استنشاق', '', '198', 'Budesonide', 'Novartis', 'Capsule', 'كبسولة', 'موسع للشعب الهوائية -- مضاد للالتهابات -- كورتيزون', 'Bronchodilator.anti-inflammatory.glucocorticoid steroid', '400mcg', 'Budesonide extended-release capsules are indicated for the treatment and maintenance of mild to moderate Crohn’s disease.[L10601,L10604] Various inhaled budesonide products are indicated for prophylactic therapy in asthma [L10607,L10613,L10619] and to reduce exacerbations of COPD.[L10619] A budesonide nasal spray is available over the counter for symptoms of hay fever and upper respiratory allergies.[L10616] Extended-release capsules are indicated to induce remission of mild to moderate ulcerative colitis[L10622] and a rectal foam is used for mild to moderate distal ulcerative colitis.[L10625] In addition, a delayed-release capsule formulation of budesonide is indicated to reduce proteinuria in adults with IgA nephropathy at risk of rapid disease progression.[L42515,L49540] Budesonide is indicated to treat eosinophilic esophagitis (EoE): For this indication, it is only approved for use in adults in Europe [L42525] while it is approved for short-term use (12 weeks) in patients 11 years of age and older in the US.[L50161]', '5010678913064', '', 16399, '2023-05-28', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
