(14140, 'Andovimpamide 150mg 10 tabs.', 'اندوفيمبامايد 150مجم 10 اقراص', '', '75', 'Lacosamide', 'Andalous pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Anti-epileptic', '150mg', 'In the US and Europe, lacosamide is indicated for the treatment of partial-onset seizures in children and adults.[L49191, L49196, L49201] In Canada, it is reserved for use in adults.[L49206]
